name: SHIFT YOUR LATITUDE
description:
TO THE AFFLUENT IN INSPIRATION I GRANT WITH THIS NON-FUNGIBLE TOKEN AN OPPORTUNITY. TO BE BETTER NOT THAN ONES DESIRES, BUT ONES ASPIRATIONS. I ASK BUT ONE THING IN RETURN. I ASK YOU TAKE THIS NON-FUNGIBLE TOKEN AS HENRY WEARS THE CROWN. FOR THOSE WITH A RESPONSIBILITY TO THEMSELVES ARE JUDGED BY THREE. THE NECK THAT IS BURDENED WITH THE WEIGHT OF RIGHTEOUSNESS, THE EGO THAT IS PLAGUED WITH GREED AND SELF-INDULGENCE, AND THE SOUL DEPUTIZED WITH RECONCILIATION OF THE MATERIAL. IF YOU WERE UNAWARE, OUR PATHS CROSSING HAVE INDEED CHANGED BOTH OUR LIVES. THE WORLD I ARGUE. IN LIEU OF SALUTATION ENTERTAINMENT THE IDEA THAT WE ARE THE CULMINATION OF EMERGENT PROPERTIES THAT CHANGED THE WORLD. WELL... WHO HAVE YOUR IMPACTED TODAY?

MINTED BY YOURS TRULY,
K @ DATADISCRETE
